title: Barood
subTitle: Anup witnesses his father's murder as a child and travels the world to track down and exact revenge against the killers. However, a New York-based detective tries to get him arrested at any cost.

title: Aadat Se Majboor
subTitle: Dinanath, a devout Hindu, wishes to get his son Shankar married to Salma, an orphan who lives with them. However, Shankar's childhood sweetheart Neetu returns to his life.

title: Yeh to Kamaal Ho Gaya
subTitle: A corrupt lawyer implicates a burglar's son in a false case of murder. Eventually, the burglar kidnaps the lawyer's son and trains him in the art of crime and burglary to exact his revenge.

title: My Life My Story
subTitle: The host invites prominent Bollywood celebrities who open up about their personal life and share interesting anecdotes based on their experiences.

title: Bhuvan Shome
subTitle: A lonely bureaucrat goes on holiday to a village in Gujarat where a young peasant woman helps him see beyond his job and develop a newfound empathy for people.

title: The Train
subTitle: An honest CBI officer must investigate a series of murders on a train. However, as he makes progress in the case, he finds disturbing leads.

title: Dharam Karam
subTitle: Shankar, a criminal, switches his newborn son with another baby, hoping to provide him with a better life. Years later, Shankar's plan backfires and causes the opposite of what he intended.

title: Humjoli
subTitle: Gopaldas, a villager, dreams of becoming rich and, thus, marries Roopa, an heiress. However, his greed knows no bounds when he plots Roopa's murder to inherit her property.

title: Teri Meherbaniyan
subTitle: Ram, an honest man, falls in love with a woman named Bijli and goes on to help the people of her village. However, the region's corrupt leader, Thakur Vijay Singh, soon begins to plot against him.

title: Kasam Suhaag Ki
subTitle: Troubles arise for Surajmukhi after her husband, Sultan, is gunned down and she and her daughter get abducted by goons. She tries her best to get revenge and escape with her child.

title: Prem Kahani
subTitle: Rajesh, an apolitical poet, is in love with Kamini and leads a peaceful life. However, when his brother is killed by the British government, he decides to become a revolutionary and joins the freedom struggle.

title: Phir Wohi Dil Laya Hoon
subTitle: Due to a rift in their relationship, Jamuna leaves her husband and takes her son Mohan with her. Years later, her husband announces that his son has returned, unaware that the man is an imposter.

title: Mausam
subTitle: A medical student nurtures a secret relationship with a woman during his college days. Several years later, he faces a rude shock after finding his illegitimate daughter involved in the flesh trade.

title: Dastaan-E-Rafi
subTitle: Renowned celebrities discuss the life journey of gifted singer Mohammed Rafi, sharing moments and incidents they experienced with him during his career.

title: Shikar
subTitle: A man is killed when he tries to molest a girl. She absconds with the police on her trail and meets a man who tries to help her find the real murderer.

title: Mere Hamdam Mere Dost
subTitle: A young man falls in love with a rich heiress posing as a poor girl. Appalled by her deception, he severs ties with her. Soon he learns the shocking truth behind his father's death.

title: Mother India
subTitle: Radha, a poor but righteous woman, struggles to raise her children opposing Sukhilala, a greedy moneylender. Despite the hurdles, she refuses to sacrifice her integrity.

title: Bobby
subTitle: Raja, the son of a rich Hindu businessman, falls in love with Bobby, a poor Catholic girl. Though their families try to keep them away from each other, they strive to be together.

title: Andhaa Kanoon
subTitle: When his parents are killed by three men, Amar, Akbar and Anthony, Vijay teams up with a forest officer who was framed in a murder case to avenge their deaths.

title: Caravan
subTitle: Sunita, a young woman, flees from her abusive marriage when her husband tries to kill her. She joins a travelling gypsy caravan en route to Bangalore and falls in love with its driver, Mohan.

title: 36 Ghante
subTitle: Three jailed convicts break out of prison and hold a family hostage in their home. The terrorised family has to play along, for any attempt to contact the police could place them in the crossfire.

title: Banarasi Thug
subTitle: Shyam must accord with his mother's wishes to marry a girl of her choice. However, when he goes to meet the girl, he is trapped by a man who forces him to marry his daughter.
